Class Tree<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tree<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - for objects in Tree.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>
    public class Tree<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Collection<T>
    Tree is collection. User can add new Nodes to root, or to other Nodes. It's easy to create branches, this structure is fragile.
